parameters.name: UT
parameters.description: Universal Time of day represented as milliseconds after 00:00:00.000

parameters.name: MASS
parameters.description:
Mass number -                                  
                               4 for He+                                      
                              12 for C+                                       
                              14 for N+                                       
                              16 for O+                                       
                              28 for N2+ and/or CO+                           
                              30 for NO+                                      
                              32 for O2+                                      
                              44 for CO2+

parameters.name: VALT
parameters.description: Altitude above the mean surface of Venus in km

parameters.name: VLST
parameters.description: Venus local solar time in hr

parameters.name: VSZA
parameters.description: Venus solar zenith angle in degrees
